{{Top|leg}}
'''Logistics battalions''' were units attached to the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]], which supervised the complex process of bringing reinforcements and equipment to the GARs front-line formations. Along with [[Fleet Ops]], they were constantly kept updated on the status of the military's lines of supply by the [[Logistics center]] at [[Coruscant Command HQ]].

Although attached to the [[Cloning/Legends|clone]] forces of the GAR, it is not directly indicated in the evidence that the personnel of the Logistics battalions were [[Clone trooper/Legends|clone troopers]], and they may conceivably have been seconded from the [[Judicial Department/Legends|Judicial Department]] and local militias.

